BIGLARI  Trademark Information
 Biglari, Sardar
Assistance, advisory services and consultancy with regard to business planning, business analysis, business management, business organization, marketing and customer analysis; branding services, namely, consulting, development, management and marketing of brands for businesses and/or individuals; business consulting services; business management services; franchising, namely, consultation and assistance in business management, organization and...
Investment services, namely, investment advice and consulting services related thereto; franchising services, namely, providing financial information regarding the establishment and/or operation of restaurants, and consultation in relation thereto; financial services, namely, financial analysis and consulting services related thereto; financial management
Restaurant services




