This is a brand page for the BIGLARI trademark by Biglari, Sardar 
                                in San Antonio, TX, 78257.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this BIGLARI trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Biglari, Sardar of the BIGLARI trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the BIGLARI trademark.
                           






On Friday, March 01, 2013,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        BIGLARI by 
                        Biglari, Sardar, San Antonio, TX  78257.
                        The USPTO has given the BIGLARI 
                        trademark serial  number of  85864621.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is STATEMENT OF USE OFFICE ACTION, CLARIFICATION NEEDED.
                        The correspondent listed for BIGLARI is 
                        
                        
                                            GREGORY B. COY of 
                                            TAFT STETTINIUS & HOLLISTER, LLP,  ONE INDIANA SQUARE, SUITE 3500, INDIANAPOLIS, IN 46204 
                                .
                            The BIGLARI trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Advertising,  Business & Retail Services
                                , 
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                , 
                                    Restaurant and Hotel Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for BIGLARI 
                            is Assistance, advisory services and consultancy with regard to business planning, business analysis, business management, business organization, marketing and customer analysis; branding services, namely, consulting, development, management and marketing of brands for businesses and/or individuals; business consulting services; business management services; franchising, namely, consultation and assistance in business management, organization and promotion; business management advisory services relating to franchising; franchising services, namely, offering business management assistance in the establishment and/or operation of restaurants. 
                            





