		materials; transportable buildings of metal; materials of metal for railway
		tracks; non-electric cables and wires of common metal; iron mongery, small
		items of metal hardware; pipes and tubes of metal; safes; goods of common metal
		not included in other classes; ores.
View Category



Machinery
Machines and machine tools; motors and engines
		(except for land vehicles); machine coupling and transmission components
